content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Standard Endpoint Protection, Server & Workload Protection, and Endpoint Sensor now support Windows 11 (24H2) November 29, 2024—The Trend Vision One Endpoint Security agent now supports Windows 11 (24H2) for Standard Endpoint Protection, Server & Workload Protection, and Endpoint Sensor-only deployments.
